quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"(Taa, Siin, Miim) hari yewtanooma fii yeru majje ka fu…ó…óoode Simoore Albaqara."
  26,2,"∆äen ko Aayeeje Alqur'aanaare …ďannginde seerndunde hakkunde Goonga kan e meere nden."
  26,3,"Belajo'o -an Nulaa…óo- sabu rer…óugol maa…óa fii fewnugol …ďe a waray wonkii maa…óa kin sabu suno e rer…óugol fii fewnugol …ďe."
  26,4,"Si Men Muuyii jippinngol Maande e ma…ď…ďe immorde ka kammu Men jippinay nde e ma…ď…ďe, daa…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen √Īalla yankinanaade nde hara ko …óe hoyu…óe, kono Men Muuyaali …óum ka ndarndagol …ďe: Mbela…ďe gom…óinay ko wirnii kon?"
  26,5,"Arataa e …ďee sirkoo…ďe immorde e waaju fu…ó…óaa- ngu jippineede immorde ka Hinnorante On e Hujjaaji maggu tinndin…ói …óin fii Ngootimmbaaku Makko e Goongugol Annabaajo Makko on si wanaa …ďe …óuuroto gaayi jentagol mo e goongin- gol mo."
  26,6,"Gom…óii …ďe fennii ko Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addani …ďe kon, aroyay e ma…ď…ďe goonginal kumpital ko …ďe wonunoo jalkitude kon, Lepte …óen jippoo e ma…ď…ďe."
  26,7,"∆Āee luttay e deppitagol e dow keefeeru ma…ď…ďe hara …ďe ndaaraali faade e leydi ndin no foti hewde ko Men fu…óini e mayri immorde e kala noone e nooneeji pu…ói fotu…ói ndaarugol …óuu…óu…ói nafoore?!"
  26,8,"Pellet, wonii e fu…óinngol ka leydi pu…ói luutondir…ói nooneeji daliili …ďanngu…óo fii Hattannde On fu…óin…óo …ói e dow wurnitugol may…ďe …ďen, …ďur…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe wonaali gom…óin…ďe."
  26,9,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo go…ó…óo foolataa Mo, ko O Yurmetee…óo jeyaa…ďe makko …ďen."
  26,10,"JaŇčto -an Nulaa…óo- tuma nde Joomi maa…óa noddunoo Muusaa ko O Yamir…óo mo yo o aru ka yim…ďe too√Īir…ďe …ďen yeddugol ma…ď…ďe Alla e maccin…óinngol yim…ďe Muusaa …ďen."
  26,11,"∆Āen ko yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďen, yo o yamir …ďe e hoore no newori kulol Alla e …óoftaade Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitaade ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin."
  26,12,"Muusaa (yo o his) maaki: "Min dey, mi…óo huli wata …ďe fennan e nder ko mi yottinta e ma…ď…ďe kon Nulal maa…óa ngal""
  26,13,"∆Āernde am nden …ďittoo sabu ko …ďe fennatan mi kon, …óemngal am ngal soko fii wowlugol, awa Nulu Jibriila (yo o his) faade e kotoo am Haaruuna fii yo o wonu walloowo lam."
  26,14,"No wonani …ďe e dow am bakkaatu sabu warugol qibtiyankoojo, mi…óo huli wata …ďe warto lam."
  26,15,"Alla Daalani Muusaa (yo o his): "wanaa non, …ďe warataa ma, yaadu e kotoo maa…óa Haaruuna wonndude e Aayeeje Amen tinndin…óe …óen e goongugol moo…óon. Pellet, Menen Me…óen wonndiri e moo…óo ballal ngal e semmbinngol ngol ko Men jentii…ďe ko wowloton kon e ko wowlante …óon kon, hay e huunde e …óum fuutotaako Men."
  26,16,"Aree ka Fir'awna, wi'anon mo: "Menen …óoo …ói…óo ko men Nulaa…ďe e maa…óa immorde ka Jooma tageefooji …óin fow.""
  26,17,"Fii yo a accitu …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen …ďen, wonndude e amen."
  26,18,"Fir'awna wi'ani Muusaa (yo o his): "Enee, men ne'aano ma ka amen …óoo hari ko o penuujo, √Īii…ďu…óaa hakkunde duu…ďi e ngurndam maa…óam, ko hommbo yamirmaa nodditagol Annabaaku?""
  26,19,"Gollu…óaa fiyaake maw…óe tuma waruno…óaa qibtiyankoojo on fii jinngngol gorko jeyaa…óo ka yim…ďe maa…óa, an ko a yeyaa…óo e yeddu…ďe neemaaji am …óin e dow maa…óa."